# Agent Global Hub

Canonical source of truth for shared agent configuration. Both Kilo Code and Antigravity read from here via symlinks.

**Rule**: Edit files HERE. Symlinks propagate changes to both agents automatically.

## Structure

```
~/.agent_global/
├── rules/global_rules.md          → symlinked to Kilo + Antigravity
├── workflows/
│   ├── core-directives.md         → symlinked to Kilo + Antigravity
│   ├── commit-protocol.md         → symlinked to Kilo + Antigravity
│   ├── memory-bank-protocol.md    → symlinked to Kilo + Antigravity
│   └── documentation-sync.md      → symlinked to Kilo + Antigravity
├── skills/
│   ├── mcp-builder/               → symlinked to ~/.kilocode/skills/
│   └── skill-creator/             → symlinked to ~/.kilocode/skills/
└── templates/memory-bank/         Bootstrap template for new projects
```

## Symlink Map

| Canonical Source | Kilo Code Target | Antigravity Target |
|-----------------|------------------|-------------------|
| `rules/global_rules.md` | `~/.kilocode/rules/global_rules.md` | `~/.gemini/GEMINI.md` |
| `workflows/*.md` (×4) | `~/.kilocode/workflows/*.md` | `~/.gemini/antigravity/global_workflows/*.md` |
| `skills/*` (×2) | `~/.kilocode/skills/*` | N/A (not supported) |

